 to further information there was no reason for us to give a postponement. }
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af5\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af5\langfe255\hich\f5\fs24\lang1033\loch\f5\fs24\lang1033 
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-360\cf1\f5\lang1033\f5\fs24\f5\lang1025\qj 26.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\cf1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls1\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-360\rtlch\af5\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af5\langfe255\hich\f5\fs24\lang1033\loch\f5\fs24\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f5\fs24\lang1033\i0\b0 Having denied the two applications for further information and a postponement we accordingly invited the various parties to address us on the substantive merits of the proposed transaction, relying on the information already in their possession.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af5\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af5\langfe255\hich\f5\fs24\lang1033\loch\f5\fs24\lang1033 
